                       |BKB-= |CKBHide |BKB=-
               
|MKOThe quintessential Thiefly hiding skill.  This command will
allow you to turn invisible for a limited amount of time.  
Being invisible costs 20 sps per use, and an additional 15 sps
per minute invis. Your degree of invisibility will be
dependent on the level standing of the potential victim you
are hiding from. The higher you advance within the guild
ranks will aid in shortening the level gap at which a 
potential victim may discover you lurking in the shadows.

|CKOGLVL required: |GKB11
|CKOSyntax: |YKOhide <on/off>               |CKOCost: |WKO20+
